WEBVTT

00:01.510 --> 00:03.083
I couldn't get pregnant.

00:03.084 --> 00:05.099
And we decided to
look for an egg donor.

00:05.100 --> 00:06.012
They chose me.

00:06.013 --> 00:07.880
I am your real mother.

00:11.295 --> 00:12.503
Lori came to the house?

00:12.504 --> 00:14.312
She gave me this picture of you.

00:14.313 --> 00:16.640
I know things, David did
a number on both of us.

00:16.641 --> 00:18.064
She said something strange.

00:18.065 --> 00:19.911
What did she mean by that?

00:21.000 --> 00:27.074
